title: TutsPlus - Go Further With WooCommerce Themes
description: WooCommerce provides a lot of power and flexibility for simple storefronts out of the box, but to build truly outstanding sites, we have to dig a little deeper. In this course, Tuts+ instructor Rachel McCollin will teach you how to enhance your WooCommerce site with features such as embedded video, mega menus and filter menus. These will create a polished and compelling sales experience for your visitors and let them connect most readily with the products they're interested in
